org.dspace.curate
Class ResolvedTask

java.lang.Object
  org.dspace.curate.ResolvedTask

public class ResolvedTask
extends java.lang.Object

ResolvedTask wraps an implementation of one of the CurationTask or ScriptedTask interfaces and provides for uniform invocation based on CurationTask methods.

Author:
richardrodgers

public void init(Curator curator)

Initialize task - parameters inform the task of it's invoking curator. Since the curator can provide services to the task, this represents curation DI.
